## Rules

- NEVER write or modify pages in `{{WIKI_ROOT}}/discussions/` — session-capture territory.
- NEVER modify files outside the Write Surface.
- Prefer updating existing pages; create new pages only when content is substantial.
- Do not create pages for trivial changes. LoreLake is not a changelog.
- Maintain cross-links. An unlinked page is dead weight.
- LoreLake tracks the current code state. Remove or update stale information as you go.
- **Standard 3 overrides everything**: never include credentials, secrets, PII, or any data that would harm if leaked. Full rules in `{{SCHEMA_DIR}}/code-content-standard.md`.
